<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Diplôme de victoire</title>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1a1a, #000);
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
  }

  .diplome {
    width: 600px;
    padding: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #fff8dc, #f5e6b3);
    border: 12px solid #c9a24a;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .diplome:before,
  .diplome:after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border: 4px solid #c9a24a;
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: -25px;
  }

  .diplome:before {
    left: -25px;
  }

  .diplome:after {
    right: -25px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: #7a4f00;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .message {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .code {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #fff;
    background: #7a4f00;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 25px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: 40px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #555;
  }

  .sparkle {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="diplome">
  <h1>🎉 Bravo ! 🎉</h1>

  <div class="message">
    Vous avez réussi à vaincre ce jeu Simon !<br>
    Votre mémoire et votre concentration sont exemplaires.
  </div>

  <div class="message">
    Voici le code pour certitude :
  </div>

  <div class="code">SIMON</div>

  <div class="signature">
    Diplôme officiel de réussite 🏆
  </div>

  <div class="sparkle">✨ Félicitations ✨</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
